OL,3,CThousands raised for 'amazing wife and
OL,4,Cmother' who died when van hit her car
OL,6,FThe family of an "amazing wife and
OL,7,Fmother" who died in a crash in Swindon
OL,8,Fhave paid tribute to her.
OL,10,FSarah Jayne Crook, 38, died when a
OL,11,FVauxhall Vivaro van collided with her
OL,12,FToyota Aygo on the A419 near White
OL,13,FHart Roundabout on Friday 5 June.
OL,15,FNearly #30,000 has been raised towards
OL,16,Fher funeral costs through an online
OL,17,Fcrowdfunder.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
