OL,3,CThousands raised for 'amazing wife and
OL,4,Cmother' who died when van hit her car
OL,6,FIn a statement, Sarah's family said:
OL,7,F"On Friday 5th June, we lost an
OL,8,Famazing wife, mother, sister,
OL,9,Fdaughter, aunt and friend, Sarah Jayne
OL,10,FCrook, to a tragic collision.
OL,12,F"We've been overwhelmed by the
OL,13,Foutpouring of love and respect for her
OL,14,Fand the support for ourselves.
OL,16,F"We would like to say thank you to the
OL,17,Fhundreds of people who have sent
OL,18,Fcondolences and memories of her.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
